quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Darngal ngal …ďattiima, lewru ndun kadi se'ekiima"
  54,2,"Si …ďe nji''ii Ma'ande, …ďe …óuurnoo …ďe mbi'a: ""Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu""."
  54,3,"∆Āe njeddi, …ďe njokki mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe. Hara le hu'unde kala no mari √Īii…ďirde."
  54,4,"GooŇč…óii kumpite arii e ma…ď…ďe, …óe ka…óitor…óum woni e mum;"
  54,5,"[∆äuum] ko √Īe√Ī∆īal jottiingal. Kono jeertingol ngol nafaani."
  54,6,"Sel …ďe. √Ďande noddoowo on noddoyta e hu'unde a√Īiniinde."
  54,7,"ja'as…ďe ndaar…óe, hi…ďe njaltira e genaale …óeen wano kanuuji caratoo…ói."
  54,8,"he√Īanii…ďe noddoowo on. He'efer…ďe …ďeen mbi'a: ""Ndee ko √Īalaande sa…ótunde""."
  54,9,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe nuuhu …ďeen yedduno. ∆Āe njedfi jiyaa…óo Amen on, …ďe wi'i : ""Ko jinnaa…óo!"", o kammbanaa."
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, won'de : ""Miin on ko mi poolaa…óo, faabo [kam]""."
  54,11,"Min ngudditiri dammbu…óe kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam,"
  54,12,"Min puccitiri leydi ndin …ďulli. Ndiye …óern fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde."
  54,13,"Min ndoondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peŇče,"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka amen. ∆äuum ko njo…ďdi [Nuuhu] jeddanoo…óo oon."
  54,15,"GooŇč…óii Min ngaccirii [kon ko Min mba…ói …ďe] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi baajitoray…óo?"
  54,16,"Tesko ko hono lepte Am e jeertingol (am) wa'anoo?"
  54,17,"GooŇč…óii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitor…óo?"
  54,18,"Aadi'en njedduno. Taskee ko hono lepte am e jeertingol (sm) wa'anoo?"
  54,19,"Min ngurtu e ma…ď…ďe henndu sa…ótundu, e √Īalaande hiitaande, duumiinde;"
  54,20,"hindu bippitira yim…ďe …ďeen, wa si tawii ko …ďe da∆ī∆īe tamaro irtaa…óe."
  54,21,"Taskee ko hono lepte am …óen e jertingol (am) ngol wa'anoo?"
  54,22,"GooŇč…óii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitor…óo?"
  54,23,"Samuuda'en njedduno waajo ngo,"
  54,24,"…ďe mb'i: ""Kere ko ne…ó…óo gooto e amen woni ko min njokkata? Haray min ngonii on tumba e nderr majjere e tamperere."
  54,25,"Hara ko e makko jaŇčtoore nden wernaa hakkunde amen? Si ko woni, ko penoowo nii, townitii…óo""."
  54,26,"Aray …ďe ngaannda (√Ďalnde) Janngo, ko hommbo woni penoowo toownitii…óo on."
  54,27,"Ko Min wurtiroo…ďe ngelooba ndewa ba ngam, jarribagol …ďe. Aynitu …ďe, mu√Ī√Īo…óaa."
  54,28,"Humpitu …ďe won'de ndiyam …óam ko sennndaa…óam hakkunde ma…ď…ďe [e ngelooba ba]; kala yaray ge…óal mum."
  54,29,"∆Āe noddi gon'diijo ma…ď…ďe, o jonni [kaafa kan], o sodi [ba]."
  54,30,"Teskii ko hono lepte am …óeen e jeertingol (am) ngol wa'anoo?"
  54,31,"Ko ha'acaango wooturu tun Min ngurti e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mba'i wa ledde yo'orude muncaa…óe."
  54,32,"GooŇč…óii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitor…óo?"
  54,33,"Yim…ďe Luutu …ďen njedduno jeertine …óeen."
  54,34,"Min ngurtuno henndu kaa∆īe e ma…ď…ďe, si wonaa e …ďeynguure Luutu nden, Min da…óndirno …ďeen ka wenndo,"
  54,35,"mo∆ī∆īere immorde e Amen. Ko non Min nko…ďitirta kala kettu…óo [neema Allah on]."
  54,36,"GooŇč…óii le o jeretinirno …ďe nanngal amen cattungal ngal. Kono …ďe cikkitii jeertinol ngol."
  54,37,"GooŇč…óii …ďe …óa…ď…ďirno mo [bonidugol e ho…ó…ďe makko …ďeen]. Min mehi gite ma…ď…ďe …óeen. ""Mee…óee lepte …óeen e jeertingol am ngol""."
  54,38,"GooŇč…óii ko bimmbi law, woni ko lepte duumii…óe ndawirani …ďe."
  54,39,"""Mee…óee lepte e jeertingol am""."
  54,40,"GooŇč…óii Min newinirii Alqur'aanare nden baajitorgol. Hara wooday baajitor…óo?"
  54,41,"GooŇč…óii jeertinaango ngon arii e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen."
  54,42,"∆Āe njeddi aayeeje amen …óen fof. Min nanngiri …ďe, nanngal poolu…óo kattan…óo."
  54,43,"Ko he'efer…ďe mon …ďen …ďuri …ďeya mo∆ī∆īude? Kaa ko da…ógol woodani on ka ∆äeri?"
  54,44,"Kaa hara …ďe mbi'ay : ""Minen ko min dental wallindiroo…ďe""?"
  54,45,"Aray nde dental [ma…ď…ďe] ngal foolee, …ďe ndunntina …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe."
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darnga ngo woni kammbaa ma…ď…ďe on, Ko Darnga noon …ďuri mawnude e haa…óude."
  54,47,"Pellet, bon…ďe …ďen ngonii e majjere e ooyunge."
  54,48,"√Ďande …ďe daasiroytee je'ece ma…ď…ďe …óeen ka nder Yiite, (…ďe mbi'anee): ""Mee…óee meemugol Saqara""."
  54,49,"Minen Min tagir hu'unde kala e e…ď…ďoore,"
  54,50,"Yamiroore amen wonaani, si wonaa [konngol] gootol pet, [yaawira] wa hin∆īaango yiitere."
  54,51,"GooŇč…óii Min kalkiino yeradii…ďe mon. Hara wooday baajitoray…óo?"
  54,52,"Kala hu'unde nde …ďe ngolli no ka ndeer …óeri,"
  54,53,"kala kadi toksum e mawnukum, ko binndaa …óum."
  54,54,"Pellet, gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďren ngonii e Aljannaaji e caatli,"
  54,55,"e toolorde goonga, ka Laam…óo kattan…óo."
